Welcome to the study! The goal for each of the 4 discussions is for you to attempt to reach a consensus on the given topic. Each discussion will be in a new channel. When you believe the topic of discussion has reached a satisfactory conclusion and you agree with it, please send a message with a ‘thumbs up’. If you have any difficulty with anything, you can message me privately at any time via the “Direct messages” section, left of screen.
